---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const schemas = [{
  "@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"TouristTrip",
  "name":"4-Day Safari: Tarangire, Serengeti, Ngorongoro",
  "description":"Four-day Tanzania safari covering Tarangire, Serengeti and Ngorongoro.",
  "provider":{"@id":"https://gokilimanjarotreks.com/#organization"},
  "touristType":"Wildlife safari traveller",
  "url":"https://gokilimanjarotreks.com/safaris/4-day-tarangire-serengeti-ngorongoro"
}];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="4-Day Safari: Tarangire, Serengeti, Ngorongoro | Go Kilimanjaro Treks"
  description="Four-day Tanzania safari covering Tarangire, Serengeti and Ngorongoro."
  schemas={schemas}
>
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="page-hero-eyebrow">Tanzania Safari Itinerary</span>
    <h1>4-Day Safari: Tarangire, Serengeti, Ngorongoro.</h1>
    <p>Four-day Tanzania safari covering Tarangire, Serengeti and Ngorongoro.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Request a Quote &#x2192;</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/255677917500" class="btn-ghost" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#x1F4AC; WhatsApp Nelson</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-white">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:820px">
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">4 Days / 3 Nights Tanzania Wildlife Safari</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">A Short Journey Through Tanzania's Most Iconic Wildlife Destinations</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Starting From USD 1,450 Per Person.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Rates depend on season, accommodation category, and group size.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Day 1: Arrival in Tanzania - Welcome to Arusha</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Upon arrival at Kilimanjaro International Airport (JRO), you will be warmly welcomed by your professional safari guide and transferred to your accommodation in Arusha, the gateway to Tanzania's famous northern safari circuit.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Surrounded by the lush landscapes of Mount Meru, Arusha offers the perfect introduction to Tanzania's natural beauty and warm hospitality. Depending on your arrival time, you may choose to relax at the lodge, enjoy the peaceful gardens, or simply recover from your journey while preparing for the exciting adventure ahead.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: River Trees Inn</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: HB</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Day 2: Tarangire National Park - Land of Giants</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">After breakfast, depart for Tarangire National Park, one of Tanzania's most scenic wildlife destinations, renowned for its enormous elephant herds and iconic baobab trees.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">As you explore the park, you will encounter a rich variety of wildlife including lions, giraffes, zebras, wildebeests, buffaloes, and numerous bird species. The Tarangire River serves as a permanent water source, attracting animals throughout the year and creating exceptional game-viewing opportunities.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Enjoy a full day game drive through this beautiful wilderness before proceeding to your lodge for dinner and overnight stay.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Country Lodge Karatu</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: FB</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Day 3: Ngorongoro Crater - Africa's Natural Wonder</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Today you journey to the spectacular Ngorongoro Conservation Area, home to the world-famous Ngorongoro Crater, often referred to as the Eighth Wonder of the World.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Descend over 600 meters into the crater floor where an incredible concentration of wildlife thrives within this natural sanctuary. The crater hosts lions, elephants, buffaloes, hippos, hyenas, wildebeests, zebras, and the endangered black rhino, offering one of the best wildlife experiences in Africa.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Enjoy a picnic lunch surrounded by breathtaking scenery before continuing your exploration of the crater floor. In the afternoon, ascend the crater walls and return to your lodge for relaxation and an unforgettable final evening in Tanzania's safari country.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Country Lodge Karatu</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: FB</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Day 4: Departure - Farewell to Tanzania</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">After breakfast, enjoy a relaxed morning before beginning your drive back to Arusha.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Depending on your departure schedule, there may be time for a brief stop in the city for shopping or cultural experiences before continuing to Kilimanjaro International Airport (JRO) for your onward flight.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">As your safari comes to an end, you leave Tanzania with unforgettable memories of magnificent wildlife, stunning landscapes, and authentic African hospitality.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: BB</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">END</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Ready to <em>Plan This Safari</em>?</h2>
    <p>Talk to Nelson about your dates, group size, and what you most want to see. He responds personally within 24 hours.</p>
    <div class="cta-actions">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary" style="font-size:1.05rem;padding:18px 40px">Request a Quote &#x2192;</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/255677917500" class="btn-wa" style="font-size:1rem" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#x1F4AC; WhatsApp Now</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>
